Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Goddamned corpse!\N--Stay down, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you getting in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--We're going after him!\N--You stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll take him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kariaena Island. The city of San-Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This city is the "front door" separating\Nthe Earth and a strange other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A mixture of different races and\Ndiverse cultures, haves and have-nots...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the shadows of all this\Nchaos lurked countless crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The San-Teresa Metropolitan Police maintained
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a special unit to deal with these crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you just sliced him\Nopen alone, Miss Don Quixote.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't occur to you to arrest him\Nso we could question him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He was being controlled via mildey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we did capture him,\Nwe wouldn't have been able to learn anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mildey?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic. Magic to control the dead, in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was devoured by evil {\i1}latena{\i0}\Nand turned into a living corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're trying to talk your way out\Nof this by blaming some weird spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're interfering with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess. Somebody doesn't want\Nus finding out the deal with this fairy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and they sent you to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much they're\Npaying you to do it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your first and last warning,\NKae Imatoeba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Never insult me in that manner again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll kill you. I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the words of a lowly Earthling\Nlike me tick you off that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious about arresting\Nwhoever's behind this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting back that fairy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are we yelling and\Npointing weapons at each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I hear you when you say\Nhe was being controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Another guy like him almost killed me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why didn't you say so earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me. I'm not your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei, want to guess what I found?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the report, Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what they've got in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The man here, who killed your partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and this man here, who almost killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them were dead before they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about their blood oxygen\Nand lactic acid levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them should've been dead\Nafter you shot them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but for some reason kept moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then only after that did they get\Nthe numbers a dead person should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they have in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're like zombies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I'm not sure what\Nthe definition of "zombie" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see any signs of major drug use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They both seemed to drink and smoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but both were in practically perfect health.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilarna Exedilica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A knight of Mirvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a guest from the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for magic, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.\NI'm completely sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He smells of evil latena.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's latena?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Latena is latena.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of magical energy source or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The latena of a fairy\Nwarped through some horrible method.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They ingested it on a regular basis,\Nand it turned them into dead men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about a drug? From Semani?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fairy dust?\NThese guys were regular users, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you call the dead "regular users," then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marzaney Sect has spells\Nthat can control the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that would explain why\Nit didn't show up on my tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That drug is one big mystery to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All we know is that it's made from fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To do this to a noble fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What terrible people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can you use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called mildey. And I can use a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then follow the trail of this latena stuff.\NLike a police dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to lack imagination, Kae Imatoeba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mildey is powerful, but not {\i1}all{\i0}-powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pound that fact into\Nwhat little brains you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good advice from a noble but useless woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So um, are you two not friends, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it looks that way, that's probably the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone out there\Nwho does like this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm curious. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my ex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's an ex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is when the attack occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Either they were watching Alvarez\Nor there was a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No way to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's any number of possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you don't have to worry\Nabout our brave knight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even know how to make a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I do too. I read it in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Wow, you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, so yeah.\NI'll be keeping my reports to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We do this the boring way.\NBut well, it's late. We'll start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you staying? I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any trouble, so just go\Nstraight to your room and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like one. That's why I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 26, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 18 in Earth years. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so damn cold tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I got kicked out of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you can't bring weapons into the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They demanded to hold on to my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let them hold on to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To a knight, a sword is every bit\Nas valuable as their life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then sleep on the ground somewhere.\NNot my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The sleeping quarters at\Nthe police station are always full.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of people there don't like Semanians.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm not going to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want any rumors or scandal\Nor things that could hurt my honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just don't tell anybody!\NShut up, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in. You can get your stuff later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you putting that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a cat allergy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kae!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I meant the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the word for it in my language.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of that kae--no, cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's an allergy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have trouble breathing when I'm around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a genetic thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you keeping a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're full of questions, aren't you?\NGive me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,About three months ago, I think it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a drug dealer that I was chasing\Nhit her when she was a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught the guy, and she survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody else in the department wanted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm keeping her temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you've got a cat allergy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can I do?\NIt was partially my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for someone to take her,\Nbut with no luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kei, but this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"You're a good kitty, Kuroi."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kae Imatoeba, you're more\Nof a softie than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I threw an injured cat out in the cold,\NI'd have trouble sleeping at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing it for myself in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm the same as the cat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, back to the park with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll stay here. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this kae.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, find a place to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let Kuroi in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei Matoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually was feeling a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, "Good night" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Good night."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Good night."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She was making fun of my name
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I keep you waiting, Mr. Kareem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not waste time, Mr. Elbaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cash payment is great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay us the rest when you get the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to those poor fairies,\Nwe can all live the good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That car, for instance. It's 300,000 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These sneakers are 3,000 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can have a good time\Nwith a girl for three dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth girls are all about looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They're easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only interested in the product.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zelada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You called, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kareem, allow me to\Nintroduce you to Zelada the Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's this wizard you were telling me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The greatest in the world\Nwhen it comes to controlling the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words honor me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply do what I can\Nfor the sake of my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "the dead."\NDoes he mean users of fairy dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My magics have not the slightest\Neffect on those who are pure of soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's where this comes in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the fairy bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A prototype, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to test it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I called them here. Using 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I said something about suspicious\Npeople making a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hands above your heads, all of you!\N--Don't look at the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it takes effect instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the verdict, Zelada?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked, my lord.\NThe two of them are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Make 'em salute, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have one shoot the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor bastard! He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Make him dance on the hood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Zelada, looks like you don't\Nknow how to dance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilarious, huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How many can be controlled by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Five thousand? Ten thousand?\NHowever many you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The most I've ever controlled at once is 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a prototype.\NThe finished product will be even more amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're using the entire body of a powerful fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The blast radius should be...\Nfive kilometers or so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the size of a nuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use this to overthrow\Nthe government of a superpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it however you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to rent Zelada too, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it ready for you,\Nso make sure you've got the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, what should we do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the first time I've been\Npallbearer for a coworker,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but you know, it's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The force has lost three people this month.\NMorale's in the gutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:18:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But the city council's trying\Nto cut our budget even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't see the reality. The bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Focus on the job in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it long?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Was what long?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your relationship with the deceased.\NYou were his partner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess. Rick was a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He and I never did agree on which\Nbaseball team to support, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In my country, it's said that\Nthose who are mourned by many
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,go to a country of eternal,\Npeaceful spring after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably what will\Nhappen to Detective Fury.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to make me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you should\Nsay at times like this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dasch zanna." "Thank you," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei, got a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Jamie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a patrol car went missing last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The one from precinct 22, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was found in Eastrock Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with two dead officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that they were killed\Nat a construction site in Redmoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They were brought here in their\Npatrol car and then thrown into the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure it's murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,From the angle of the bullet wound,\Nthis one looks like suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure. We'll have to wait\Nfor the autopsy to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have our police dog take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tilarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you remembered my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take a look at the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonah Tilarna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I told you to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are dead.\NJust like the assassin and the dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So they were regular users of fairy dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys were cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If a cop's using, his coworkers\Nare gonna notice right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they used gold jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold jewelry can be used as a catalyst\Nto enhance the power of latena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you wanted something\Nwith this kind of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't have a mistake\Nthe width of a human hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the best craftsmen\Nin my country couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a human couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about a digitally\Ncontrolled manufacturing device?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many people are buying\Npowerful manufacturing machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I found someone using a dummy corporation. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dennis Elbaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A Semanian club owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell does a guy like that\Nwant with a manufacturing device?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything! We need to\Ncapture him and question him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth is ruled by a god named\N"fundamental rights."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We need some proof to convince a judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to do the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Her life is on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Her? You mean the fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like this is personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not care if that fiel, that fairy, dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own responsibility towards her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You going to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was more important than her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Next time"\NNext time on {\i1}COP CRAFT{\i0}.
